data.description: This beautiful all brick 2 story custom built 4-bedroom home is sitting on open 1+ acre lot w/ No restrictions, No HOA & No City taxes! Walk to Lake Benson! Primary suite downstairs with spacious on suite that has separate tub and shower, double vanity, Granite counters & spacious walk-in closet. The first floor has real Oak hardwood flooring throughout. Spacious kitchen w/ granite countertops & bar. Extra-large bonus room upstairs, great for kids’ playroom or movie room! Two car side entry garage. Lots of storage in the walk-in attic. An amazing yard for entertaining guest, kids to play and pets to run. Roof, gutter shield, crawl space and more are new or updated in the last three years.
